She loked at him and looked at the glass. "Energin Nothing big."
She slammed the rest of the glass and got up for another.  She sat 
back down, really feeling it now. 
"Yeah, hookey. I'll twain dem. But you kot to elp." She slammed the 
drink in one swallow.
